<https://ontologist.ai/ns/oe/module/kilo-node-modules-which-changelog-md/interior> {
    <https://ontologist.ai/ns/oe/module/kilo-node-modules-which-changelog-md> db:content """# Changes


## 2.0.2

* Rename bin to `node-which`

## 2.0.1

* generate changelog and publish on version bump
* enforce 100% test coverage
* Promise interface

## 2.0.0

* Parallel tests, modern JavaScript, and drop support for node < 8

## 1.3.1

* update deps
* update travis

## v1.3.0

* Add nothrow option to which.sync
* update tap

## v1.2.14

* appveyor: drop node 5 and 0.x
* travis-ci: add node 6, drop 0.x

## v1.2.13

* test: Pass missing option to pass on windows
* update tap
* update """ ;
        db:title "CHANGELOG" .
}

