    <https://ontologist.ai/ns/oe/module/github-skills-acquire-codebase-knowledge-assets-templates-conventions-md> db:content """# Coding Conventions

## Core Sections (Required)

### 1) Naming Rules

| Item | Rule | Example | Evidence |
|------|------|---------|----------|
| Files | [RULE] | [EXAMPLE] | [FILE] |
| Functions/methods | [RULE] | [EXAMPLE] | [FILE] |
| Types/interfaces | [RULE] | [EXAMPLE] | [FILE] |
| Constants/env vars | [RULE] | [EXAMPLE] | [FILE] |

### 2) Formatting and Linting

- Formatter: [TOOL + CONFIG FILE]
- Linter: [TOOL + CONFIG FILE]
- Most relevant enforced rules: [RULE_1], [RULE_2], [RULE_3]
""" ;
        db:title "CONVENTIONS" ;
        oe:fileExt ".md" ;
        oe:fileName "CONVENTIONS.md" ;
        oe:filePath ".github/skills/acquire-codebase-knowledge/assets/templates/CONVENTIONS.md" ;
        oe:fileSizeBytes 1354 .
}

